\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--tip block-link--long\">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Tip: <\/strong>Plaka is a great place to stay on your trip to Milos. It&#x2019;s close to many of the top things to do in Milos, and it&#x2019;s home to beautiful churches, museums, and island walking paths.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/12083758\/milos-plaka1.jpg\" alt=\"milos island greece plaka\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"milos island greece plaka\" class=\"wp-image-60095 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/12083758\/milos-plaka1.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/12083758\/milos-plaka1-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/12083758\/milos-plaka1-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/12083758\/milos-plaka1-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/12083758\/milos-plaka1-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/12083758\/milos-plaka1-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/12083758\/milos-plaka1-144x180.jpg 144w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/12083758\/mil