e shapes, bridges, and archways for you to jump off and explore from. There&#x2019;s also a shipwreck to take photos of and swim out to. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can get there by bus or by renting an ATV or moped and zooming across the island.&#xA0;&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--tip \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Tip:<\/strong> Wear bright colors and get some awesome photos of you standing against the white rock and the blue sea. <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/tips\/travel-photography-tips\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Read more travel photo tips<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/12083808\/milos-sarakiniko-1.jpg\" alt=\"milos greece sarakiniko beach\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"milos greece sarakiniko beach\" class=\"wp-image-60097 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/12083808\/milos-sarakiniko-1.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/12083808\/milos-sarakiniko-1-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/12083808\/milos-sarakiniko-1-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/12083808\/milos-sarakiniko-1-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/12083808\/milos-sarakiniko-1-24x30.jp