/li><\/ul><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<ul><li><strong>Fyriplaka Beach <\/strong>&#x2013; A wide horseshoe bay with soft white sand and rocks at the shore. Because of the rocks and exposed position, you get more waves here, making it fun to swim.<\/li><li><strong>Alogomandra Beach<\/strong> &#x2013; A sandy cove that is sandwiched between flat white rock cliffs.<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-2 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/14130455\/milos-beaches2-540x810.jpg\" alt=\"milos greece best beaches\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"milos greece best beaches\" data-id=\"60224\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/14130455\/milos-beaches2.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/?attachment_id=60224\" class=\"wp-image-60224 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/14130455\/milos-beaches2-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/14130455\/milos-beaches2-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/14130455\/milos-beaches2-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/14130455\/milos-beaches2-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/14130455\/milos-beaches2-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/14130455\/milos-beaches2-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/14130455\/milos-beaches2-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.c