d breathtaking sea, make it one of the most beautiful beaches in Milos to visit. Climb down the ladder to reach the beach itself!<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Most of the beaches on Milos are close together, so it&#x2019;s easy to visit most of them during your visit. Some of the more remote beaches don&#x2019;t have good roads leading to them. Because of this, be prepared that you may have to drive down dirt tracks or walk quite a bit to the beach.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/12133149\/milos-greece-beaches1.jpg\" alt=\"beaches milos greece\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"325\" alt=\"beaches milos greece\" class=\"wp-image-60163 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/12133149\/milos-greece-beaches1.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/12133149\/milos-greece-beaches1-800x578.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/12133149\/milos-greece-beaches1-1080x780.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/12133149\/milos-greece-beaches1-450x325.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/12133149\/milos-greece-beaches1-30x22.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/12133149\/milos-greece-beaches1-163x118.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/12133149\/milos-greece-beaches1-249x180.jpg 249w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/12133149\/milos-greece-beaches1-768x555.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/12133149\/milos-greece-beaches1-1024x740.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/20