Eat<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Greek food is delicious with colorful salads, olives, and fresh seafood. There are great restaurants and cafes spread over the entire island, however, most of the options are in Plaka, Trypiti, and Adamantas (at the port).&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Our favorite restaurants in Milos were:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Glaronisia (Greek)<\/li><li>Kayak Cafe (Delicious coffee and breakfast)<\/li><li>Medusa (Seafood &amp; Greek)<\/li><li>Phatses (Lovely atmosphere)<\/li><li>Pizzeria Stasi (Pizza)<\/li><li>Methismeni Politeia (Mediterranean)<\/li><li>Bakalikon Galanis (Greek)<\/li><li>Kivotos ton Gefseon (Cafe, Desserts)<\/li><li>Hanabi Seaside (Sushi)<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-2 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/15132000\/milos-greece-restaurants1-540x810.jpg\" alt=\"greek food\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"greek food\" data-id=\"60254\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/15132000\/milos-greece-restaurants1.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/?attachment_id=60254\" class=\"wp-image-60254 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/15132000\/milos-greece-restaurants1-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/15132000\/milos-greece-restaurants1-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/15132000\/milos-greece-restaurants1-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/15132000\/milos-greece-restaurants1-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/15132000\/milos-greece-restaurants1-109x163.jpg