eece\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">More about the car rental options<\/a>)<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--transport \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--transport\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.ferryhopper.com\/en\/?aff_uid=slthr\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Check the ferry tickets and prices here<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/15132020\/milos-island-greece-ferry.jpg\" alt=\"greek islands ferry\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"300\" alt=\"greek islands ferry\" class=\"wp-image-60258 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/15132020\/milos-island-greece-ferry.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/15132020\/milos-island-greece-ferry-800x534.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/15132020\/milos-island-greece-ferry-1080x721.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/15132020\/milos-island-greece-ferry-450x300.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/15132020\/milos-island-greece-ferry-30x20.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/15132020\/milos-island-greece-ferry-163x109.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/15132020\/milos-island-greece-ferry-270x180.jpg 270w, 